Text:
it's always a treat to see quality music posted here. there are many people posting super-pop (not that there's anything wrong with that) but to find obscure, talented performers here makes my day.

this is a testament to the power of p2p networks. google may want to index the world, but we can make all the world's information free, as it should be.

thank you. and please go see justin live and buy some swag when you're there-- support up and coming artists!
i'd love to see him...but i live in Europe...so, if he ever comes my way i'll be there!
this just downloaded in 1and a half minutes!
